show.description: A modern-day girl accidentally time-travels to a mysterious, beastly realm and is forced to marry the cold, mysterious Wolf King. While trying to find a way back home, she gradually falls in love with him. Amid palace politics, secrets, and a unique fantasy world, their love story unfolds with humor, magic, and unexpected twists.
